## üìä Project Overview

**Revenue Pulse** is a 2-page Power BI dashboard built to analyze sales performance, profitability, and customer insights for a mid-size retail business.  
It demonstrates end-to-end Data Analytics and Power BI skills including data modeling, DAX calculations, time-intelligence, KPI design, interactive storytelling, and practical business problem-solving.

This project is designed to showcase capabilities for Data Analyst / BI Analyst roles and is suitable for a fresher competing with 1‚Äì2 years of experience.

