## üßÆ Key DAX Measures

Core KPIs used in the dashboard:

Total Revenue
```dax
Total Revenue = SUM(Sales_Fact[Revenue])
```

Total Profit
```dax
Total Profit = SUM(Sales_Fact[Profit])
```

Profit Margin %
```dax
Profit Margin % = DIVIDE([Total Profit], [Total Revenue])
```

Total Revenue LY (Last Year)
```dax
Total Revenue LY =
CALCULATE([Total Revenue], SAMEPERIODLASTYEAR(Calendar_Dim[Date]))
```

Total Revenue LM (Last Month)
```dax
Total Revenue LM =
CALCULATE([Total Revenue], DATEADD(Calendar_Dim[Date], -1, MONTH))
```

MoM Growth %
```dax
MoM Growth % =
DIVIDE([Total Revenue] - [Total Revenue LM], [Total Revenue LM])
```

YoY Growth %
```dax
YoY Growth % =
DIVIDE([Total Revenue] - [Total Revenue LY], [Total Revenue LY])
```

Sales Rep Performance Score
```dax
Sales Rep Performance Score =
VAR BaseRevenue = CALCULATE([Total Revenue], ALL(SalesRep_Dim))
VAR BaseProfit  = CALCULATE([Total Profit], ALL(SalesRep_Dim))
VAR BaseMargin  = CALCULATE([Profit Margin %], ALL(SalesRep_Dim))
VAR RevenueScore = DIVIDE([Total Revenue], BaseRevenue) * 50
VAR ProfitScore  = DIVIDE([Total Profit], BaseProfit) * 30
VAR MarginScore  = DIVIDE([Profit Margin %], BaseMargin) * 20
RETURN RevenueScore + ProfitScore + MarginScore
```

Revenue 3M Moving Avg
```dax
Revenue 3M Moving Avg =
AVERAGEX(
    DATESINPERIOD(Calendar_Dim[Date], MAX(Calendar_Dim[Date]), -3, MONTH),
    [Total Revenue]
)
```

